s=\"ico-feedback\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-feedback\"></use></svg><span class=\"zDocsFeedbackButtonText\"> Feedback</span></span></div></div><div class=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><button aria-label=\"Show topic actions\" data-toggle=\"dropdown\" id=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-ellipsis-h\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-ellipsis-h\"></use></svg></button><div class=\"dropdown-menu zDocsDropdownMenu zDocsTopicActionsMobileDropdown dropdown-menu-right\"></div></div><div style=\"flex-basis: 100%; height: 0px;\"></div><ul class=\"zDocsTopicPageDetails\"><li class=\"zDocsTopicPageDate css-cinqea\">Last Updated<span class=\"css-cinqea\">Apr 25, 2023</span></li><li class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryDetailsItem\"><button class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryButton\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-topic-summary\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-topic-summary\"></use></svg>Summarize</button></li><li class=\"spacer\" role=\"presentation\"></li><div class=\"zDocsLabelWrapper\"><ul><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: Uniface\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=prod_uniface\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>Uniface</a></li><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: 10.4\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=uniface_10.4\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>10.4</a></li></ul></div></ul></header><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBody\" data-prismjs-copy=\"Copy\" data-prismjs-copy-error=\"Copy failed! Use Ctrl + C instead.\" data-prismjs-copy-success=\"Copied!\"><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBodyContent\" dir=\"ltr\"><div id=\"zDocsAiSummaryContaineruniface_104lrx1665702881630_2.html\"></div><div><article class=\"hascomments\" data-page=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/lrx1665702881630_2.html\" id=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/lrx1665702881630_2.html\"><main role=\"main\"><article aria-labelledby=\"ariaid-title1\" class=\"dita\" id=\"lrx1665702881630\" role=\"article\">\n<h1 class=\"title topictitle1\" id=\"ariaid-title1\">upostmsg.dll\n   </h1>\n<div class=\"body conbody\" id=\"lrx1665702881630__upostmsg_dll_521556\"><p class=\"shortdesc\">Implementation of the Message Utility. Applications can call this API directly.\n </p>\n<section class=\"section refsyn\" id=\"lrx1665702881630__topic_d176636e1_d176637e1_d176638e1\">\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"lrx1665702881630__p_d176639e1_d176640e1_d176641e1\">The function interface is:</p>\n<div class=\"code-toolbar\"><pre class=\"pre language-plaintext\" tabindex=\"0\"><code class=\"language-plaintext\">int UPostMessage (\nchar * <var class=\"keyword varname\">NetworkPath</var> : IN\nchar * <var class=\"keyword varname\">Destination</var> : IN\nchar * <var class=\"keyword varname\">MessageID</var> : IN\nchar * <var class=\"keyword varname\">MessageData</var> : IN\n)\n</code></pre><div class=\"toolbar\"><div class=\"toolbar-item\"><button class=\"copy-to-clipboard-button\" data-copy-state=\"copy\" type=\"button\"><span>Copy</span></button></div></div></div>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"lrx1665702881630__topic_d141497e1_d141498e1_d141499e1_d141500e1_d141501e1\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d959172e74\">Parameters </h2>\n<ul class=\"ul\">\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"lrx1665702881630__li_d53867e1_d53868e1_d53869e1\">\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"lrx1665702881630__p_d176645e1_d176646e1_d176647e1\"><var class=\"keyword varname\">NetworkPath</var>—path to the\n                  Uniface Router:</p>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"lrx1665702881630__p_d176648e1_d176649e1_d176650e1\">\n<var class=\"keyword varname\">HostID</var>{<code class=\"ph codeph\">+</code>\n<var class=\"keyword varname\">PortNumber</var>}<code class=\"ph codeph\">|</code>\n<var class=\"keyword varname\">UserName</var>.</p>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"lrx1665702881630__li_d53870e1_d53871e1_d53872e1\"><var class=\"keyword varname\">Destination</var>—name of the\n               targeted component instance:<p class=\"p\" id=\"lrx1665702881630__p_d176654e1_d176655e1_d176656e1\"><var class=\"keyword varname\">InstPath</var>\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">:</code> {<var class=\"keyword varname\">InstName</var>}.</p><ul class=\"ul\">\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"lrx1665702881630__li_d53873e1_d53874e1_d53875e1\"><var class=\"keyword varname\">InstPath</var>—Uniface Server\n                     Type (UST)</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"lrx1665702881630__li_d53876e1_d53877e1_d53878e1\"><var class=\"keyword varname\">InstName</var>—name of the\n                     component instance. If not present or if no component instance with the\n                     specified name can be found in the receiving application, it is delivered to\n                     the receiveMessage trigger of the application shell.</li>\n</ul></li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"lrx1665702881630__li_d53879e1_d53880e1_d53881e1\"><var class=\"keyword varname\">MessageID</var>—identifier for the\n               message. It must contain at least one non-blank character. Trailing blanks are\n               ignored.</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"lrx1665702881630__li_d53882e1_d53883e1_d53884e1\"><var class=\"keyword varname\">MessageData</var>—data of the\n               message. When this is not a single string, enclose the message in double quotes\n                  (<code class=\"ph codeph\">\" \"</code>).</li>\n</ul>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"lrx1665702881630__p_d176669e1_d176670e1_d176671e1\">The maximum lengths of these parameters are given in the table below.</p>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"lrx1665702881630__topic_d141502e1_d141503e1_d141504e1_d141505e1_d141506e1\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d959172e152\">Return values </h2>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"lrx1665702881630__p_d176675e1_d176676e1_d176677e1\">If successful, the return value is zero.</p>\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table class=\"table\" count-columns=\"2\" id=\"lrx1665702881630__table_d18620e1_d18621e1_d18622e1\"><caption><span class=\"table--title-label\">Table 1. </span><span class=\"title\">Message API Errors</span></caption><colgroup><col/><col/></colgroup><thead class=\"thead\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"lrx1665702881630__table_d18620e1_d18621e1_d18622e1__entry__1\">\n<p class=\"p\">Error</p>\n</th>\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"lrx1665702881630__table_d18620e1_d18621e1_d18622e1__entry__2\">Problem indication</th>\n</tr>\n</thead><tbody class=\"tbody\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"lrx1665702881630__table_d18620e1_d18621e1_d18622e1__entry__1\">-12001</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"lrx1665702881630__table_d18620e1_d18621e1_d18622e1__entry__2\">No host name specified</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"lrx1665702881630__table_d18620e1_d18621e1_d18622e1__entry__1\">-12002</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"lrx1665702881630__table_d18620e1_d18621e1_d18622e1__entry__2\">Host name too long (PM_MAXHOST)</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"lrx1665702881630__table_d18620e1_d18621e1_d18622e1__entry__1\">-12003</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"lrx1665702881630__table_d18620e1_d18621e1_d18622e1__entry__2\">No user name</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"lrx1665702881630__table_d18620e1_d18621e1_d18622e1__entry__1\">-12004</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"lrx1665702881630__table_d18620e1_d18621e1_d18622e1__entry__2\">User name too long (PM_MAXUSER)</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"lrx1665702881630__table_d18620e1_d18621e1_d18622e1__entry__1\">-12005</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"lrx1665702881630__table_d18620e1_d18621e1_d18622e1__entry__2\">No instance path specified</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"lrx1665702881630__table_d18620e1_d18621e1_d18622e1__entry__1\">-12006</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"lrx1665702881630__table_d18620e1_d18621e1_d18622e1__entry__2\">Instance path too long (PM_MAXUST)</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"lrx1665702881630__table_d18620e1_d18621e1_d18622e1__entry__1\">-12007</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"lrx1665702881630__table_d18620e1_d18621e1_d18622e1__entry__2\">Instance name too long (PM_MAXINSTANCE)</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"lrx1665702881630__table_d18620e1_d18621e1_d18622e1__entry__1\">-12009</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"lrx1665702881630__table_d18620e1_d18621e1_d18622e1__entry__2\">Message ID too long (PM_MAXMSGDATA)</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"lrx1665702881630__table_d18620e1_d18621e1_d18622e1__entry__1\">-12011</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"lrx1665702881630__table_d18620e1_d18621e1_d18622e1__entry__2\">Message data too long (PM_MAXMSGDATA)</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"lrx1665702881630__table_d18620e1_d18621e1_d18622e1__entry__1\">-12017</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"lrx1665702881630__table_d18620e1_d18621e1_d18622e1__entry__2\">Initialize Socket failed</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"lrx1665702881630__table_d18620e1_d18621e1_d18622e1__entry__1\">-12018</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"lrx1665702881630__table_d18620e1_d18621e1_d18622e1__entry__2\">Send string to the server failed</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"lrx1665702881630__table_d18620e1_d18621e1_d18622e1__entry__1\">-12019</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"lrx1665702881630__table_d18620e1_d18621e1_d18622e1__entry__2\">Receive TCP Message failed</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody></table></div>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"lrx1665702881630__topic_d141507e1_d141508e1_d141509e1_d141510e1_d141511e1\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d959172e302\">Description </h2>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"lrx1665702881630__p_d176681e1_d176682e1_d176683e1\">The <span class=\"ph filepath\">upostmsg.dll</span> contains the implementation of the Message Utility. It provides the functionality for the <span class=\"ph filepath\">umsgutil.exe</span> program by way of the Uniface <span class=\"keyword apiname\">upostmessage</span> function. Applications can call this API directly. Additionally, the <span class=\"ph filepath\">upostmsg.lib</span> library, located in the <span class=\"ph filepath\">3gl/lib</span> subdirectory, is provided for linking purposes.</p>\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table class=\"table\" count-columns=\"3\" id=\"lrx1665702881630__table_d18623e1_d18624e1_d18625e1\"><caption><span class=\"table--title-label\">Table 2. </span><span class=\"title\">Message API limits</span></caption><colgroup><col/><col/><col/></colgroup><thead class=\"thead\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"lrx1665702881630__table_d18623e1_d18624e1_d18625e1__entry__1\">Parameter description</th>\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"lrx1665702881630__table_d18623e1_d18624e1_d18625e1__entry__2\">Literal name</th>\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"lrx1665702881630__table_d18623e1_d18624e1_d18625e1__entry__3\">Limit</th>\n</tr>\n</thead><tbody class=\"tbody\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"lrx1665702881630__table_d18623e1_d18624e1_d18625e1__entry__1\">Host name</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"lrx1665702881630__table_d18623e1_d18624e1_d18625e1__entry__2\">PM_MAXHOST</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"lrx1665702881630__table_d18623e1_d18624e1_d18625e1__entry__3\">128</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"lrx1665702881630__table_d18623e1_d18624e1_d18625e1__entry__1\">User name</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"lrx1665702881630__table_d18623e1_d18624e1_d18625e1__entry__2\">PM_MAXUSER</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"lrx1665702881630__table_d18623e1_d18624e1_d18625e1__entry__3\">128</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"lrx1665702881630__table_d18623e1_d18624e1_d18625e1__entry__1\">Instance path</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"lrx1665702881630__table_d18623e1_d18624e1_d18625e1__entry__2\">PM_MAXUST</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"lrx1665702881630__table_d18623e1_d18624e1_d18625e1__entry__3\">16</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"lrx1665702881630__table_d18623e1_d18624e1_d18625e1__entry__1\">Instance name</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"lrx1665702881630__table_d18623e1_d18624e1_d18625e1__entry__2\">PM_MAXINSTANCE</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"lrx1665702881630__table_d18623e1_d18624e1_d18625e1__entry__3\">16</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"lrx1665702881630__table_d18623e1_d18624e1_d18625e1__entry__1\">MessageID</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"lrx1665702881630__table_d18623e1_d18624e1_d18625e1__entry__2\">PM_MAXMSGID</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"lrx1665702881630__table_d18623e1_d18624e1_d18625e1__entry__3\">32</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"lrx1665702881630__table_d18623e1_d18624e1_d18625e1__entry__1\">Message data</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"lrx1665702881630__table_d18623e1_d18624e1_d18625e1__entry__2\">PM_MAXMSGDATA</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"lrx1665702881630__table_d18623e1_d18624e1_d18625e1__entry__3\">512</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"lrx1665702881630__table_d18623e1_d18624e1_d18625e1__entry__1\">Port number</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"lrx1665702881630__table_d18623e1_d18624e1_d18625e1__entry__2\">PM_MAXPORTNR</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"lrx1665702881630__table_d18623e1_d18624e1_d18625e1__entry__3\">8</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"lrx1665702881630__table_d18623e1_d18624e1_d18625e1__entry__1\">DNP</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"lrx1665702881630__table_d18623e1_d18624e1_d18625e1__entry__2\">PM_MAXDNP</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"lrx1665702881630__table_d18623e1_d18624e1_d18625e1__entry__3\">16</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody></table></div>\n</section>\n</div>\n</article></main></article>\n</div></div><div class=\"contentPlaceholder\" style=\"height: 500px;\"><div class=\"contentContainer zDocsSideBoxes\"><div><h5 aria-level=\"5\" class=\"css-g931ng\">Related Links</h5><ul><li><a class=\"css-ettsdk\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/nhr1665702690996.html\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-related-link\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-related-link\"></use></svg>umsgutil.exe</a><p>Command line interface for the Message API Utility.</p></li><li><a class=\"css-ettsdk\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/wtd1665702577667.html\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-related-link\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-related-link\"></use></svg>postmessage</a><p>Send a message from one component instance to another.</p></li><li><a class=\"css-ettsdk\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/uyo1665702691073.html\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-related-link\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-related-link\"></use></svg>Message API Utility</a><p>The Message API Utility sends messages to a Uniface application from a non-Uniface Windows application using Uniface's remote postmessage mechanism.</p></li></ul></div></div></div></div><div class=\"bottomFeedback\"><div aria-labelledby=\"bottomFeedbackText\" class=\"bottomFeedbackContent\" role=\"group\"><span class=\"bottomFeedbackText\" id=\"bottomFeedbackText\">Was this topic helpful?</span><div class=\"bottomFeedbackButtonGroup\"><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_4094377\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-up\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-up\"></use></svg><span>Like</span></a><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_4094377\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-down\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-down\"></use></svg><span>Dislike</span></a></div></div></div><div style=\"position: fixed; bottom: 170px; right: 70px; cursor: pointer; transition-duration: 0.2s; transition-timing-function: linear; transition-delay: 0s; z-index: 3; opacity: 0; visibility: hidden; transition-property: opacity, visibility;\"><button aria-label=\"Scroll to top\" class=\"zDocsScrollTopBtn\" data-tooltip-content=\"Scroll to top\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsBackToTopToolTip\" id=\"zDocsScrollToTop\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-next\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-next\"></use></svg></button></div></body></html>", "text": "upostmsg.dll Add to My Topics Add selected topic and subtopics Add Topic & Subtopics with topic head Add entire publication Watch Download PDF Save selected topic Save selected topic and subtopics Save entire publication Share Email Link Copy Link Feedback Last Updated Apr 25, 2023 Summarize Uniface 10.4 upostmsg.dll Implementation of the Message Utility. Applications can call this API directly. The function interface is: int UPostMessage ( char * NetworkPath : IN char * Destination : IN char * MessageID : IN char * MessageData : IN ) Copy Parameters NetworkPath —path to the Uniface Router: HostID { + PortNumber } | UserName . Destination —name of the targeted component instance: InstPath : { InstName }. InstPath —Uniface Server Type (UST) InstName —name of the component instance. If not present or if no component instance with the specified name can be found in the receiving application, it is delivered to the receiveMessage trigger of the application shell. MessageID —identifier for the message. It must contain at least one non-blank character. Trailing blanks are ignored. MessageData —data of the message. When this is not a single string, enclose the message in double quotes ( \" \" ). The maximum lengths of these parameters are given in the table below. Return values If successful, the return value is zero. Table 1. Message API Errors Error Problem indication -12001 No host name specified -12002 Host name too long (PM_MAXHOST) -12003 No user name -12004 User name too long (PM_MAXUSER) -12005 No instance path specified -12006 Instance path too long (PM_MAXUST) -12007 Instance name too long (PM_MAXINSTANCE) -12009 Message ID too long (PM_MAXMSGDATA) -12011 Message data too long (PM_MAXMSGDATA) -12017 Initialize Socket failed -12018 Send string to the server failed -12019 Receive TCP Message failed Description The upostmsg.dll contains the implementation of the Message Utility. It provides the functionality for the umsgutil.exe program by way of the Uniface upostmessage function. Applications can call this API directly. Additionally, the upostmsg.lib library, located in the 3gl/lib subdirectory, is provided for linking purposes. Table 2. Message API limits Parameter description Literal name Limit Host name PM_MAXHOST 128 User name PM_MAXUSER 128 Instance path PM_MAXUST 16 Instance name PM_MAXINSTANCE 16 MessageID PM_MAXMSGID 32 Message data PM_MAXMSGDATA 512 Port number PM_MAXPORTNR 8 DNP PM_MAXDNP 16 Related Links umsgutil.exe Command line interface for the Message API Utility. postmessage Send a message from one component instance to another. Message API Utility The Message API Utility sends messages to a Uniface application from a non-Uniface Windows application using Uniface's remote postmessage mechanism. Was this topic helpful? Like Dislike"}